- If `native` format is selected ‚Üí `"‡§Æ‡•á‡§∞‡•á ‡§™‡§æ‡§∏ ‡§¶‡•ã ‡§∏‡•å ‡§∞‡•Å‡§™‡§Ø‡•á ‡§π‡•à"`.

```python
payload = {
    "input": "‡§Æ‡•Å‡§ù‡•á ‡§ï‡§≤ 9:30am ‡§ï‡•ã appointment ‡§π‡•à",
